* Sat Jul 6 20:08:10 2013 -0400

    Apparmor profile for DNSCrypt
    
    On systems that support apparmor this file can be dropped into /etc/apparmor.d/apparmor.profile.dnscrypt-proxy
    
    On reboot it should be active. aa-status to confirm,
    aa-enforce /etc/apparmor.d/apparmor.profile.dnscrypt-proxy
    if it doesn't enforce after reboot.

